    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab><note><note>Il <rs key="#Princeps">principe</rs>
                                <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/303">Arechi II</persName>
                                offre al monastero di S. Sofia di <placeName
                                    key="#Uncertain_tradition #Cities #Fiscal_property #Allocation_to_churches #Rent_in_money"
                                    ref="#places/110">Benevento</placeName>
                            </note>(prosegue l'elenco iniziato con il doc. 3535):</note></ab> <ab>(…) [61] Concessimus et iam dicte <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/85"
                            >Sancte Sophie <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs></orgName> ut
                        habeat ex sacro nostro <rs key="#Palatium">palatio</rs>
                        <rs
                            key="#Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Allocation_to_churches #Rent_in_money #Slave_labour"
                            >annualiter auro soledos duocentos</rs> pro vestito comparandum aut quod
                        inibi opus fueriti, nec non etiam et hoc statuere visi sumus ut nostra
                        concessione sit firma in nominato <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>.
                        (…)</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="editions">
                <p><emph>Editions</emph>: IS1 VIII, col. 581B ; IS2 VIII, coll. 32C; IS2 X-2, col.
                    428C; Borgia 1769, I, pp. 298-301; Cappelletti 1845, p. 44; CSS, I, 1 [61], pp.
                    331-332(source of the text reproduced here). <emph>Document summaries</emph>: Di
                    Meo 1795-1819, III, p. 97; Bertolini O, 1926, 72; RIM, 455.</p>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="additional">
                <p/>
            </div>
            <div type="bibliography" subtype="links">
